"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"文人就係文人<br />\n講野真係精闢<br />\n<br />\n諗起Snowden對privacy&amp;監控嘅評論（反駁唔做錯野唔怕監控），有異曲同工之妙<br />\n&quot;Saying you don't need privacy because you have nothing to hide is like saying you don't need freedom of speech because you have nothing to say.&quot;"},{"pid":"83bfbd76315f8811c8a9f0b944a8847c3a196eda","tid":1510212,"uid":223525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ceede0e2b754b46278d359bae9ddff71bfc794c","tid":1510212,"uid":271395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲心入面果句係「你唔反抗咪冇事囉」"},{"pid":"850efc4eeacde48a9164b13b8c66dc0a50eaa557","tid":1510212,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77080b65607026d8cc4273044573d56485bd80db","tid":1510212,"uid":37715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"犯法咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8001678d1bb6b8abcd949b9e89a2cc6d68960c4e","tid":1510212,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ceede0e2b754b46278d359bae9ddff71bfc794c","tid":1510212,"uid":271395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲心入面果句係「你唔反抗咪冇事囉」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n一日唔死<br />\n一日都叫無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}